<HEAD>Masked Attackers Kill Woman In Nablus; 15 Wounded</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 12 grafs to UPDATE with 15 wounded, details, army
denying involvement in Monday death; picks up 9th pvs: Ms. Boulus'...;
