   A woman and three children were found
slain in a home at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac Tuesday after her
husband turned back efforts by relatives to see her for two days,
police and neighbors said.
   The husband, 36-year-old Lee Artis Carter, was taken into
custody and transported to a hospital for cuts on his wrists caused
