dispatched to search the aircraft, he said.
   Rosado was taken to the Metropolitan Correctional Center in
south Dade County to await a federal hearing Wednesday.
   The passengers were to travel on to San Juan Tuesday night
aboard different carriers, airline spokesman Ed Stewart said from
American headquarters in Fort Worth, Texas.
